      static class  HwmfMisc.WmfRestoreDc
      The META_RESTOREDC record restores the playback device context from a previously saved device context.(Meta_RESTOREDC记录从之前保存的设备上下文恢复播放设备上下文。)
      static class  HwmfMisc.WmfSaveDc
      The META_SAVEDC record saves the playback device context for later retrieval.(Meta_SAVEDC记录保存播放设备上下文以供稍后检索。)
      static class  HwmfMisc.WmfSetBkColor
      The META_SETBKCOLOR record sets the background color in the playback device context to a specified color, or to the nearest physical color if the device cannot represent the specified color.(Meta_SETBKCOLOS记录将播放设备上下文中的背景色设置为指定的颜色，或者如果设备无法表示指定的颜色，则设置为最近的物理颜色。)
      static class  HwmfMisc.WmfSetBkMode
      The META_SETBKMODE record defines the background raster operation mix mode in the playback device context.(Meta_SETBKMED记录定义播放设备上下文中的背景格栅操作混合模式。)
      static class  HwmfMisc.WmfSetLayout
      The META_SETLAYOUT record defines the layout orientation in the playback device context.(Meta_SET LAYOU记录定义播放设备上下文中的布局方向。)
      static class  HwmfMisc.WmfSetMapMode
      The META_SETMAPMODE record defines the mapping mode in the playback device context.(Meta_SET MAPMED记录定义播放设备上下文中的映射模式。)
      static class  HwmfMisc.WmfSetMapperFlags
      The META_SETMAPPERFLAGS record defines the algorithm that the font mapper uses when it maps logical fonts to physical fonts.(Meta_SETMAPPERFLAGS记录定义字体映射程序在将逻辑字体映射到物理字体时使用的算法。)
      static class  HwmfMisc.WmfSetRelabs
      The META_SETRELABS record is reserved and not supported.(Meta_SEDRELABS记录已保留且不支持。)
      static class  HwmfMisc.WmfSetRop2
      The META_SETROP2 record defines the foreground raster operation mix mode in the playback device context.(META_SETopp 2记录定义了播放设备上下文中的前景格栅操作混合模式。)
      static class  HwmfMisc.WmfSetStretchBltMode
      The META_SETSTRETCHBLTMODE record defines the bitmap stretching mode in the playback device context.(Meta_SETSTRETCHBLTMODE记录在播放设备上下文中定义位图拉伸模式。)
